<hr />
<p>Hey, Henzoid and Crocket here, thanks so much for reading our dumbassery! Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1722371&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1570900257" alt="Shaggydredlocks" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1722371)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;">Shaggydredlocks</a></span>, author of the original &quot;When Day Breaks&quot;, who graciously gave us permission to demolish his 001 proposal.<br />
Thanks to the following cool kids for giving us critique<br />
- <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2858989); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1570900257" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2858989); return false;">Westrin</a></span><br />
